Here's a standard `.gitignore` file for a Next.js project. You should place this file in the root directory of your Next.js application.

```
# dependencies
/node_modules
/frontend/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.js

# testing
/coverage

# next.js build output
/.next/
/out/

# production
/build

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# local env files
.env*.local
.env
.vercel/
```